## 🎯 OVERVIEW

### Form Architecture
- **Type:** Single-file HTML app (client-side only, no backend)
- **Views:** 3 screens — Dashboard → Form Wizard → Preview & Submit
- **Task types:** 18 distinct accounting workflows grouped in 6 categories
- **Output:** Markdown (for AI) OR JSON (for audit trail)

### User → AI Workflow
```
[User] opens HTML → selects task → fills form → clicks "Copy to AI"
  ↓
[Clipboard] contains markdown-formatted text
  ↓
[User] pastes into chat with AI Accounting Controller
  ↓
[AI] parses, validates, creates journal entry, saves file
  ↓
[AI] responds with confirmation + links to saved files
```

